snippet: Before the troubled rollout of HealthCare.gov, Gary M. Cohen repeatedly told Congress that it would work well.
abstract: Gary M Cohen, official in charge of federal health insurance marketplace HealthCare.gov, says he is resigning; he repeatedly told Congress before its troubled rollout that it would work well.
lead_paragraph: Before the troubled rollout of HealthCare.gov, Gary M. Cohen repeatedly told Congress that it would work well.
